HOW TO INSTALL
===============

- Unzip and upload (or vice-versa should you be that way inclined)


- Modify quicksnaps_app/config/config.php as needed
    [line 14] $config['base_url']
    [line 26] $config['index_page']


- Modify quicksnaps_app/config/database.php
    - [lines 40-45]


- Make sure the 'uploads' directory is writeable


- Point your browser to where you have installed QuickSnaps and set up admin account


- Enjoy!
